  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist the Next Turnip Boy Game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/f73d66889a9a9a041e3761bb125219f1.avif?t=1758380512\" width=617 height=150 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/f55ea5d04892660344a388a7712d73bd.poster.avif?t=1758380512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/f55ea5d04892660344a388a7712d73bd.webm?t=1758380512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>Take control of an adorable turnip who happens to be an absolute menace to society.</strong> After failing to pay taxes and getting evicted from your home, you must go on an epic quest to pay back your massive debt to Mayor Onion. Solve plantastic puzzles, meet eccentric vegetables and fruits, and take on treacherous fights against animals both big and small. Along the journey, uncover what’s spoiling this garden community, and rise to tear down the corrupt vegetable government! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/c65e6c71be336e57a80f6fb574c6eceb.avif?t=1758380512\" width=617 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- A thrilling single player adventure full of tax evasion, petty crimes and more.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/dde4d7a71143ff9b4622209701c4025a.poster.avif?t=1758380512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/dde4d7a71143ff9b4622209701c4025a.webm?t=1758380512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- A large cast of quirky food-based characters, all with their own stories and problems.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/e1ee88e1862e83bcbd37cc6773295b3a.poster.avif?t=1758380512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/e1ee88e1862e83bcbd37cc6773295b3a.webm?t=1758380512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Tons of tax documents to rip up, allowing you to erase your paper trail and potentially destroy the government!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/a3f7c1ea5aec23d57b29061c563397e8.poster.avif?t=1758380512\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1205450/extras/a3f7c1ea5aec23d57b29061c563397e8.webm?t=1758380512\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p>",
